{"tha-ap459:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap459:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap459:0.3":"Ekachattiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap459:1.1":"“Angarajata pathavi, ","tha-ap459:1.2":"kukkulanugata mahi; ","tha-ap459:1.3":"Padumuttaro bhagava, ","tha-ap459:1.4":"abbhokasamhi cankami. ","tha-ap459:2.1":"Pandaram chattamadaya, ","tha-ap459:2.2":"addhanam patipajjaham; ","tha-ap459:2.3":"Tattha disvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap459:2.4":"vitti me upapajjatha. ","tha-ap459:3.1":"Mariciyotthata bhumi, ","tha-ap459:3.2":"angarava mahi ayam; ","tha-ap459:3.3":"Upahanti mahavata, ","tha-ap459:3.4":"sarirassasukhepana. ","tha-ap459:4.1":"Sitam unham vihanantam, ","tha-ap459:4.2":"vatatapanivaranam; ","tha-ap459:4.3":"Patigganha imam chattam, ","tha-ap459:4.4":"phassayissami nibbutim. ","tha-ap459:5.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap459:5.2":"padumuttaro mahayaso; ","tha-ap459:5.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap459:5.4":"patigganhi tada jino. ","tha-ap459:6.1":"Timsa kappani devindo, ","tha-ap459:6.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap459:6.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap459:6.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap459:7.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap459:7.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap459:7.3":"Anubhomi sakam kammam, ","tha-ap459:7.4":"pubbe sukatamattano. ","tha-ap459:8.1":"Ayam me pacchima jati, ","tha-ap459:8.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap459:8.3":"Ajjapi setacchattam me, ","tha-ap459:8.4":"sabbakalam dhariyati. ","tha-ap459:9.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap459:9.2":"yam chattamadadim tada; ","tha-ap459:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap459:9.4":"chattadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap459:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap459:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap459:10.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap459:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap459:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap459:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap459:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap459:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap459:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap459:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekachattiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap459:14.1":"Ekachattiyattherassapadanam sattamam. "}